- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning from partial feedback in a specific AI application (machine translation). 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper presents a new approach to improving software (SMT systems) using bandit feedback. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with structured prediction and learning algorithms.
